2.20	Sour_Girl	Sour Girl	"Sour Girl" is a song by Stone Temple Pilots. The song was written by singer Scott Weiland and guitarist Dean DeLeo for their band's fourth album, aptly titled No. 4. "Sour Girl" also appears on the compilation albums Thank You and Buy This. It is the only STP song to enter the Billboard Hot 100 chart, peaking at number 78 . "Sour Girl" was one of STP's biggest hits since the Core and Purple era. Billboard ranked "Sour Girl" at #88 on its list of the 100 Best Rock Songs of the 2000s.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/7/71/Sourgirl.JPG/220px-Sourgirl.JPG
